<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AspireHub-<%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="guidance.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css"
    integrity="sha512-Evv84Mr4kqVGRNSgIGL/F/aIDqQb7xQ2vcrdIwxfjThSH8CSR7PBEakCr51Ck+w+/U6swU2Im1vVX0SVk9ABhg=="
    crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="nav.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="footer.css">
</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/nav.ejs') %>
        <div class="sslc-img-container">
            <div class="sslc-banner-content">
                <h1>Your Future Starts Here: Explore, Decide, Succeed!</h1>
                <h3>Smart Choices for a Bright Career!</h3>
                <div class="ban-btn">
                    <a href="#higher-secondary"><button type="button" class="btn btn-success">Higher Secondary</button></a>
                    <a href="#diploma"><button type="button" class="btn btn-success">Diploma</button></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


        <div class="vertical-box">
            <h2 class="vertical-box-h2" id="higher-secondary">Courses After 10th</h2>
            <p class="para">After completing the 10th grade, students have multiple career paths based on their
                interests and future goals. They can choose from science, commerce, arts, or opt for diploma and
                skill-based courses.</p>

            <div class="container">
                <div class="img-container"><img src="guidance-img5.jpg" alt="Image 1"></div>

                <div class="container-text">
                    <h3>🎯Higher Secondary Education (Class 11 & 12)</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li><b>Science Stream:</b> Physics, Chemistry, Biology/Mathematics (For Engineering, Medical,
                            and IT
                            fields)</li>
                        <li><b>Commerce Stream:</b> Accounts, Business Studies, Economics (For Banking, Finance, and
                            Business Management)</li>
                        <li><b>Arts/Humanities Stream:</b> History, Political Science, Sociology (For Civil Services,
                            Media,
                            and Social Work)</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="container">
                <div class="container-text">
                    <h3>🎯Polytechnic Diploma Courses</h3>
                    <div class="Polytechnic">
                        <div>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Diploma in Engineering (Mechanical, Civil, Electrical, Computer Science, etc.)</li>
                                <li>Diploma in Architecture</li>
                                <li>Diploma in Fashion Design</li>
                                <li>Diploma in Hotel Management</li>
                                <li>Diploma in Photography</li>
                                <li>Diploma in Agriculture</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="img-container"><img src="guidance-img2.jpg" alt="Image 1"></div>

            </div>

            <div class="container">
                <div class="img-container"><img src="guidance-img3.jpg" alt="Image 1"></div>

                <div class="container-text">
                    <h3>🎯ITI (Industrial Training Institute) Courses</h3>
                    <div class="Polytechnic">
                        <div>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Electrician</li>
                                <li>Fitter</li>
                                <li>Mechanic</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Plumber</li>
                                <li>Welder</li>
                                <li>Computer Operator and Programming Assistant (COPA)</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="container">
                <div class="container-text">
                    <h3>🎯Paramedical & Healthcare Courses</h3>
                    <div class="Polytechnic">
                        <div>
                            <ul>
                                <li>Diploma in Medical Lab Technology (DMLT)</li>
                                <li>Diploma in Nursing</li>
                                <li>Diploma in Radiology</li>
                                <li>Diploma in Physiotherapyt</li>
                            </ul>
                        </div>

                    </div>
                </div>
                <div></div>
                <div class="img-container"><img src="guidance-img4.jpg" alt="Image 1"></div>

            </div>

            <div class="container">
                <div class="img-container"><img src="guidance-img5.jpg" alt="Image 1"></div>

                <div class="container-text">
                    <h3>🎯Vocational & Skill-Based Courses</h3>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Certificate Course in Web Development</li>
                        <li> Certificate Course in Digital Marketing</li>
                        <li> Certificate Course in Graphic Designing</li>
                        <li> Certificate in Mobile Repairing</li>
                        <li>Certificate in Interior Designing</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>


        <div class="Horizontal-box" id="diploma">
            <h2 class="vertical-box-h2">Courses After Diploma</h2>
            <p class="para">After completing a diploma, students can either start working or pursue higher education to
                enhance their career opportunities.</p>
            <div class="horizontal-flex">
                <div class="horizontal-container">
                    <div class="horizontal-img-container"><img src="guidance-img6.jpg" alt="Image 1"></div>

                    <div class="horizontal-container-text">
                        <h5>Lateral Entry into B.Tech/B.E.</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Diploma holders can directly enter the 2nd year of a Bachelor of Technology (B.Tech) or
                                Bachelor of Engineering (B.E.) in relevant streams.</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="horizontal-container">
                    <div class="horizontal-img-container"><img src="guidance-img7.jpg" alt="Image 1"></div>

                    <div class="horizontal-container-text">
                        <h5> Bachelor's Degree Courses</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>B.Sc. (Bachelor of Science) </li>
                            <li> B.Com. (Bachelor of Commerce)</li>
                            <li> B.A. (Bachelor of Arts)</li>
                            <li> BBA (Bachelor of Business Administration)</li>
                            <li> BCA (Bachelor of Computer Applications)</li>
                            <li> B.Des (Bachelor of Design - Fashion, Interior, Product Design, etc.)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="horizontal-container">
                    <div class="horizontal-img-container"><img src="guidance-img8.jpg" alt="Image 1"></div>

                    <div class="horizontal-container-text">
                        <h5>Advanced Diploma & Certification Courses</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Advanced Diploma in Software Development</li>
                            <li> Advanced Diploma in Data Science & AI</li>
                            <li> Diploma in Aviation & Hospitality Management</li>
                            <li> Diploma in Cyber Security</li>
                            <li>Post Diploma in Machine Learning & AI</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="horizontal-container">
                    <div class="horizontal-img-container"><img src="guidance-img3.jpg" alt="Image 1"></div>

                    <div class="horizontal-container-text">
                        <h5> Government Job Exams</h5>
                        <ul>
                            <li>After a diploma, students can also appear for government job exams like Railways (RRB),
                                Staff Selection Commission (SSC), and State Government Jobs.</li>

                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="faq-box">
            <h2 class="vertical-box-h2"> Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ) – Career Guidance After 10th & Diploma</h2>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>What are the courses I can pursue after 10th?</span>
                    <span class="arrow">🔽</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    You can choose from science, commerce, or arts streams in higher secondary education (Class 11 &
                    12). You can also opt for polytechnic diploma courses, ITI courses, or vocational training based on
                    your interest.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>Are there any government exams I can appear for after completing my diploma?</span>
                    <span class="arrow">🔽</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    Yes, you can appear for Railway Recruitment Board (RRB) exams, Staff Selection Commission (SSC)
                    exams, State Public Service Commission (PSC) exams, and various other government exams like banking,
                    police, and PSU recruitment.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>What are the career options after a diploma in engineering?</span>
                    <span class="arrow">🔽</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    You can pursue a lateral entry into B.Tech/B.E. or apply for government jobs, PSUs, or private
                    sector roles like technician, design engineer, or project assistant.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>Are there online courses after the 10th?</span>
                    <span class="arrow">🔽</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    Yes, you can take online certification courses in coding, web development, digital marketing, AI,
                    and design from platforms like Coursera, Udemy, and Google Skillshop.

                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>Can I do B.Sc. after a diploma?</span>
                    <span class="arrow">🔽</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    Yes, diploma holders can pursue B.Sc. in relevant fields such as Computer Science, Electronics,
                    Hotel Management, and Fashion Designing.
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>Can I get a job in the IT sector after a diploma?</span>
                    <span class="arrow">🔽</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <ul>
                        <li>Yes, diploma holders in Computer Science, IT, or Software Engineering can work as: </li>
                        <li> Software Developers</li>
                        <li> Web Designers</li>
                        <li>Network Administrators</li>
                        <li> Database Managers</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <script>
            const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll(".faq-question");

            faqItems.forEach(item => {
                item.addEventListener("click", () => {
                    const answer = item.nextElementSibling;
                    const arrow = item.querySelector(".arrow");

                    if (answer.style.display === "block") {
                        answer.style.display = "none";
                        arrow.textContent = "🔽";
                    } else {
                        answer.style.display = "block";
                        arrow.textContent = "⬆️";
                    }
                });
            });
        </script>
        <%- include('../partials/footer.ejs') %>
</body>

</html>